HEADWORD: Phormium
<hw>Phor"mi*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. fr. Gr.
<?/ a plaited mat, a kind of plant.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A
genus of liliaceous plants, consisting of one species (<spn>Phormium
tenax</spn>). See <er>Flax-plant</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
